  "text": "Combining everything together in this manner we establish Eq. (74), where the operators are replaced by their eigenvalues for N = 2. The proof of the orthogonality of Ψ p,x can, again, be accomplished recursively. However, we spare the reader the details since they can be found in Ref. [CITATION_1] and merely quote the final result. The scalar product reads",
